<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-11-06T00:36:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-11-06T00:36:00-05:00" n="949" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d949">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/13704.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Canova</persName>
                                to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Aguascalientes</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-05T23:00:00-06:36">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1914, 11 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The Convention to-day received telegram from Carranza insisting on his
                            conditions, and telegram from Obregón asking for an extension of time
                            for Carranza so as to date the twenty days of Gutiérrez as Provisional
                            President from his assumption of office. It was decided to send
                            Carranza. telegraphic ultimatum that he deliver the Executive Power to
                            Gutiérrez by November 10, 6 p.m. General Gutiérrez will take the oath of
                            office to-morrow.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Canova</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>